tip.text: Honey roasted chicken (todays special) was pretty good
Pretty decorations
Chicken teriyaki sandwich was good. Also had Full Aussie- scrambled eggs was yummy, Wild Mushroom Ragout - taste flavorful but was bit too salty. Tiramisu cake was pretty ordinary.
Chilli soft shell crab pasta was good! Service was great too! Mains come with soup and drink during lunch.
I had curry paella it was huge, would recommend to share it with a friend or two, the taste is pretty savory and the texture is quite "creamy"
Had aglio olio, pesto and arabiata pasta, polenta and lils breakie. would recommend their pastas. The others were okok.
We had Aglio Olio &  Marathoner Big Breakfast the pumpkin bun was yum! So as the lemongrass mint👍🏼 will definitely come back again
